criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Major subject

          -  Subject who received resection with primary non-small cell lung cancer at the
             University Hospital of Angers and whose tumor samples will be stored in collection of
             biological resources of University Hospital of Angers

          -  A written inform consent.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Under 18 year old;

          -  Pregnant or nursing women;

          -  Deprived of liberty;

          -  Age under curatorship or guardianship;

          -  Unable to consent person;

          -  About not carrying a non-small cell lung cancer.
